item.title: Home
item.description:
My name is Graham and I’m a full-stack developer at Helpful.com in Toronto, Canada.

I’ve shared the code for my thesis work on GitHub. Related papers can be found in my list of publications.

Also on GitHub, a Knowledge-Based System for designing electrical inductors built for a course during my Master’s.
